 Compute Severity Signals"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Grade Severity Tier\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: info, warning, critical + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Just Record (Info) · ②→ Warn Channel (Slack) · ③→ Page Urgently (Outlook) · ④→ Archive Unscored","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"7d649f92-3c59-bbec-6e18-4e7ca08d75f7","name":"Note: Grade Severity Tier"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Just Record (Info)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,40],"id":"8ee27b67-aab2-49ec-4499-9c226dd0efb4","name":"Note: Just Record (Info)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Warn Channel (Slack)\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"f7abdb7c-a6a2-417a-0fe6-a6d2e6930d74","name":"Note: Warn Channel (Slack)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Page Urgently (Outlook)\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1000],"id":"2d9a5c4f-0fae-8034-6d04-febf816aada8","name":"Note: Page Urgently (Outlook)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Unscored\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Tier Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,1480],"id":"fe2ea22b-8e53-c1a6-3691-e7c2c57b40d0","name":"Note: Archive Unscored"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Tier Outcomes\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"02770d9e-cd05-0e7e-cadd-d94a5187d0da","name":"Note: Merge Tier Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"847e871d-d318-338b-05b0-487cba5270fa","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Send Summary to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"b7520ae1-4fe7-3fe7-d5d5-f5aea9087a24","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"b15015a3-0b5b-5125-561a-436021648dc3","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Outlook","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"2fdf8268-01ba-a7b5-b9ac-0aa48c7fa3a3","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,1540],"id":"1f78663d-9710-a741-e23a-4726d72e979d","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Notify the team on new events with Outlook automatically\n\n**Pattern:** Event Notification · **Level:** Core · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nNotify the team on new events with Outlook automatically. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual utilities is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Read Metrics from Outlook → Compute Severity Signals → Grade Severity Tier → Just Record (Info) → Merge Tier Outcomes → Align Field Names → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to event notification without manual effort\n- Anyone automating utilities in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"43f27550-4b11-4dc4-fe95-45cf23f64673","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"95afaa9c-d71b-752c-1328-73d59324ffa2","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"4710a60e-dc1e-ba3c-b846-ee4557d45b30","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your utilities process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"2e73f3e0-e679-db31-42b9-27341e1ba986","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Metrics from Outlook","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Metrics from Outlook":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Severity Signals","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Severity Signals":{"main":[[{"node":"Grade Severity Tier","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Grade Severity Tier":{"main":[[{"node":"Just Record (Info)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warn Channel (Slack)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Page Urgently (Outlook)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Archive Unscored","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Just Record (Info)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warn Channel (Slack)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Page Urgently (Outlook)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Unscored":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Tier Outcomes":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"ba789e52-6681-419c-af36-6a533f6ab390","id":"FDX05842"}